(2271)-Schumacher,N (2210) Germany 2014 1-0 (41)}) 6... Nf6 7. d3 d5 8. exd5
Nxd5 9. Nf3 Nb6 10. Ba2 Bd6 11. O-O O-O 12. Nbd2 Nf4 13. Ne4 Bg4 14. Bxf4 exf4
15. Qd2 Bxf3 16. gxf3 Be5 17. Rad1 Rc8 18. d4 {Bezgodov,A (2482)-Kurnosov,I 
(2657) Khanty-Mansiysk 2013 1/2-1/2 (71)}) (3... Nf6 4. b5 Nd4 5. c3 $15) 4.
bxc5 $11 dxc5 5. Nf3 e5 6. Bb5 {White has a cramped position} Bg4 (6... Bd6 7.
Bb2 Nf6 8. Nxe5 $11) 7. Bxc6+ bxc6 8. h3 Bh5 (8... Be6 $11) 9. c4 (9. d3 $5 $14
{is worth consideration}) 9... Qd3 {White cannot castle king side} (9... Nf6 $5
$17) 10. Qe2 Qxe2+ 11. Kxe2 f5 12. d3 (12. exf5 $2 {doesn't work because of} e4
13. g4 exf3+ 14. Kxf3 Bf7 15. Re1+ Be7 $17) 12... fxe4 13. dxe4 Bd6 14. g4 {
White threatens to win material: g4xh5} Bg6 15. Nbd2 Nf6 {Black threatens to
win material: Nf6xe4} 16. Ke3 {White king safety dropped} Rb8 17. Nh4 Bxe4 {
Decoy: e4} 18. Nxe4 (18. f3 $5 Bg6 19. Nxg6 hxg6 20. Rb1 $15) 18... Rb3+ $17
19. Ke2 Nxe4 20. Bd2 $2 (20. Nf5 $5 O-O 21. Be3 $17) 20... O-O 21. Rh2 $4 {
simply worsens the situation} (21. Nf5 $142 $19) 21... Rb2 22. Nf3 (22. Rd1 {
is not the saving move} Be7 23. Nf5 Bg5 $19 (23... Nxd2 $6 {is a useless try}
24. Rxd2 Rxd2+ 25. Kxd2 Bg5+ 26. Ke2 $17) (23... Rxd2+ $6 {is easily refuted}
24. Rxd2 Nxd2 25. Nxe7+ Kf7 26. Nxc6 Nxc4 27. Rh1 $15)) 22... Rxf3 $1 {
Deflection: d2} 23. Kxf3 Nxd2+ 24. Ke3 (24. Kg2 {doesn't get the bull off the
ice} e4 25. Rhh1 e3 $19) 24... Nxc4+ 25. Kd3 e4+ $1 {Discovered attack: e5,
Bd6xh2} 26. Kxc4 (26. Kxe4 Bxh2 {Discovered attack}) 26... Bxh2 27. Kxc5 (27.
Re1 {does not solve anything} Rc2+ 28. Kb3 Rxf2 29. Rxe4 Rf3+ 30. Kb2 Rxh3 $19)
27... Rxf2 (27... Be5 $142 {seems even better} 28. Rf1 Rc2+ 29. Kb4 Bd4 $19)
28. Kxc6 (28. Re1 {the only chance to get some counterplay} Rf3 29. Rxe4 Rc3+
30. Kb4 Rxh3 31. Kc5 $19) 28... e3 29. Kb7 e2 (29... Bg3 30. Kxa7 e2 31. Rb1
