{B23: Closed Sicilian: Lines without g3} 1. e4 c5 2. Nc3 Nc6 3. f4 g6 4. Nf3
Bg7 5. a3 a6 (5... d6 6. Bb5 Bd7 7. O-O a6 8. Bc4 Nd4 9. d3 e6 10. Nxd4 cxd4
