$18) 17... d5 $4 (17... Qh4 18. Kh1 d5 $18 (18... Rxf2 $2 {doesn't solve
anything} 19. Rg3 Qxg3 20. Qxg3 $18)) 18. e6 (18. Qh5+ Kg8 19. Rg3+ Bg4 20.
Rxg4+ Qg5 21. Rxg5#) 18... Bxe6 (18... Qh4 {a fruitless try to alter the
course of the game} 19. Rg3 Qh7 20. e7 $18) 19. Qxe6 (19. Qh6+ Kg8 20. Rg3+ Bg4
21. Rxg4+ Qg5 22. Rxg5+ Kf7 23. Re1 Rfe8 24. Qg7#) 19... Qf6 (19... Rf6 {
