26. Nb1 Nc5 $19) 25... a5 26. Rde1 (26. Nd2 {doesn't improve anything} Re6 27.
Nb1 Rd8 $19) 26... e4 27. Nd4 Nc5 28. Nc6 (28. Rd1 {doesn't get the bull off
the ice} Rad8 29. Nb5 Re5 $19) 28... Re6 29. Ne7+ (29. Rd1 {doesn't change
anything anymore} Nd3 30. Ne7+ Kh7 $19) 29... Kh7 30. Nf5 Nd3 (30... g6 {
makes it even easier for Black} 31. Ne3 $19) 31. Rb1 a4 32. b3 (32. Rd1 {
a fruitless try to alter the course of the game} Ra5 33. g4 g6 $19) 32... a3
33. Ra1 b5 34. Re3 (34. Nd4 {does not solve anything} Re5 $19) 34... Nf4 (34...
Nd5 {keeps an even firmer grip} 35. Re2 Nc3 36. Rd2 $19) 35. f3 (35. Nd4 {
